OL,3,CHoliday park closes after parts of its
OL,4,Croof torn off by strong winds
OL,6,FA video shows the moment the roof of
OL,7,Fthe Waterfront Bar at Challaborough
OL,8,FBay Holiday Park was damaged by the
OL,9,Fwindy conditions.
OL,11,FIt happened on 28 March, forcing the
OL,12,Fholiday park to close to any new
OL,13,Fguests.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said no one was hurt in
OL,16,Fthe incident but the park will be
OL,17,Ftemporarily closed until further
OL,18,Fnotice.
OL,20,FAll Easter events at the park have
OL,21,Fbeen postponed until next weekend.
