OL,3,CHoliday park closes after parts of its
OL,4,Croof torn off by strong winds
OL,6,FThe park said: "After careful
OL,7,Fconsideration and review of the
OL,8,Fadverse weather conditions here at
OL,9,FChallaborough Bay, we have made the
OL,10,Fdecision to temporarily close the
OL,11,Fholiday park for new arrivals.
OL,13,F"To allow for essential repairs, and
OL,14,Ffor the safety of everyone on park, we
OL,15,Fwould ask that our owners do not
OL,16,Ftravel to the holiday park at this
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,F"The safety of everyone on park is our
OL,20,Fmain priority."
